>>docker run redis ,will run the latest version of redis image.

(Tags)
>>docker run redis:4.0 ,will run the 4.0 version

>>docker run redis, redis:latest version run 

(Stdin)
>>docker run myApp,if myApp is taking stdin ,still this doesn't gives enter

>>docker run -i myApp ,now interative mode ,can enter.without console .

>>docker run -it myApp ,now both.

(port)

>every container have an ip 

>>docker run -p 80:5000 myApp
>>docker run -p 81:5000 myApp

(volume)

Data(/var/lib/mysql) >>mysql container 
any changes will refelect in container.

>>docker stop 
>>docker rm mysql 
all data gone .for that we need to map on our host.

>>docker run -v /opt/datadir:/var/lib/mysql mysql ,now on /opt/datadir 

(inspect)
more details about container in json format.

>>docker inspect ubuntu.

(container logs)
>>docker logs containerIdorName